Inequality r5c1 < r5c2 (c2=2). So r5c1 must be less than 2, i.e., must be 1. Since only integer less than 2 in set is 1. Therefore r5c1 =1.

Great. Row5 now missing {3,4,6}. c4 {1,3,4,6}->{3,4,6}. c5 {1,3,6}->{3,6}. c6 {1,3,4,6->{3,4,6}}.

