c2 {1,3,4}->{3,4}
c4 {1,3,4,5,6->{3,4,5,6}}
c6 {1,3,4,5,6->{3,4,5,6}}

Now column2 currently rows 1,4,6 need {1,3,4}. r6c2 {3,4}. r4c2 {3,4}. r1c2 {1,3,4}. Only 1 appears only in r1c2. Therefore r1c2 =1.

Column2 now remaining numbers {3,4} for rows 4 and 6. r4c2 {3,4}, r6c2 {3,4}. unresolved.

